This python script is intended to translate sample and biohansel code information
into a tsv file that contains a breakdown of all groups of which a sample is a member

Input:

	This script excpects a file that has the following format:
	
	Sample1	code
	Sample2	code
	Sample3	code
	...
	SampleN	code

The script requires each line to only contain the sample tab separated from the code and no other information, the script is not tolerant of trailing tabs

