This is the required format for the following step in the pipeline.

It should be noted that the supplied codes should ideally be Biohansel compatible, non-numerial characters are not supported with the exception of "."'s to indicate rank levels
If the codes contain other characters they will be given new codes in the other script, if they do not have the proper format with ranks separated with "."s then the code will fail.